{"tid":2412383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭民望跌至五個月新低","createTime":"2021-02-18T04:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T09:05:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"56d32b9219d97a53b741db750263f009e93719ce","tid":2412383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/TCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FTCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=41bb7106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FTCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE%2F&h=f2e08e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/TCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望跌至五個月新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/efKkpW6fKewIx9KJe6yzS178jgw=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4SQXTZVUYNFL5LLKH6COPIA5X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FefKkpW6fKewIx9KJe6yzS178jgw%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4SQXTZVUYNFL5LLKH6COPIA5X4.jpg&h=bfac5cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日確診數字回落但無助挽回政府民望。香港民意研究所昨發表最新特首民望，特首林鄭月娥（圖）的最新評分為31分，支持率為18%，為去年9月以來新低，反對率為70%，民望淨值達負52個百分點。有學者斥林鄭只揣摩北京意思行事，不顧香港民意，倡高官薪金應與民望水平掛鈎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n42%受訪者給予零分<br />\n<br />\n香港民研繼上月18至22日後，再於本月2至4日，由訪問員隨機抽樣電話訪問1,018名市民。兩次調查之間港府多次封區，林鄭亦曾出席由建制派掌控的立法會答問大會。調查顯示，市民對林鄭的最新評分僅31分，有42%受訪者更給予林鄭0分，其支持率為18%，為去年9月以來新低，反對率為70%，民望淨值為負52個百分點，最新評分及民望淨值分別比半個月前分別微跌1分及3個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n司長方面，財政司司長陳茂波的民望雖然為三司中最高，但評分也低至35.2分，民望淨值則為負21個百分點，比一個月前下跌7個百分點；創去年5月以來新低，其次為政務司司長張建宗，評分為31.2分，民望淨值為負31個百分點，為去年12月以來新低。至於長期民望包尾的律政司司長鄭若驊，評分只有23.8分，但已是2019年6月反修例運動以來新高，民望淨值為負50個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n浸大政治及國際關係學系副教授陳家洛指，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"230ebe88b23e96c7a28bf99f79ed1c1b5cb95f53","tid":2412383,"uid":224533,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"佢仲沉醉緊扭扭薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccf249829aecd5366621c84d48fcc2e0dbb5941","tid":2412383,"uid":147536,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"連本人都唔介意既時候<br />\n其他人睇黎都係晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c1c5beb8fc4e868c84304d65de7fb7a104f9c6","tid":2412383,"uid":7369,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"是鳩旦啦, 佢都唔撚care架啦"},{"pid":"412aa32f9e4ece2ebdd0932d6ac00616fdeeafd1","tid":2412383,"uid":77196,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"已經谷底仲有得跌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263cf34ea4f29a67d51956d9f8b1cbd8604bc456","tid":2412383,"uid":244369,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔使對市民負責, 係咁上下㗎啦"},{"pid":"d64d2438f9b143159c83420ca18e20264c447234","tid":2412383,"uid":4052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"56d32b9219d97a53b741db750263f009e93719ce","tid":2412383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/TCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FTCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=41bb7106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FTCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE%2F&h=f2e08e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/TCPGUUFVD5A3XPYTQAVNHC64QE/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望跌至五個月新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https